dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Roads_2010.gdb. [The Centerline data set is a vector representation of center of pavement in the County of Portage, Wisconsin. The centerlines are digitized from 1:12000 digital orthophotography or entered by coordinate geometry.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
